\id 1TH
\h 1 TESALONIKA
\toc1 Akɨnafarir Faragha Zuim, Pol Tesalonikan Nguibamɨn itir Sios baghava an Osiri
\toc2 1 Tesalonika
\toc3 1 Te
\mt1 Akɨnafarir Faragha Zuim, Pol Tesalonikan Nguibamɨn itir Sios baghava an Osiri
\is1 Akɨnafarir Faragh Zuim
\ip Tesalonikan nguibam, a Mesedonian Provinsɨn nguibar ekiar mam. Dughiar Pol Filipai ataghizim, a Tesalonikan ghugha nguibar kamɨn siosɨn mam okore (Ap 17:1-9). Egha Judabar garima, gumazamizir avɨrim Polɨn akam gɨn ghua egha Kraisɨn adarazir otifi, ezɨ Judaba navir kuramɨn Polɨn ikiava a gamizɨ, a Tesalonikan nguibam ataki. Egha gɨn Pol ghua Korinɨn nguibamɨn itima, a ko ingarir gumazim Timoti iza bizir Tesalonikan Kraisɨn adarazir otivizibar gun Pol mɨgei.
\ip Ezɨ Pol Timotin akam baregha, egha Tesalonikan sios nɨghnɨzir gavgaviba gavgavim me danɨngasa, a ko Sailas ko Timoti akɨnafarir kam an osirigha me bagha anemada. Fofozir gumazir avɨrim ghaze, akɨnafarir kam ti Pol osirizir akɨnafarir Godɨn Akɨnafarimɨn aven itibar faragha zuim. Ezɨ akɨnafarir kam Pol Tesalonikabar nɨghnɨzir gavgaviba ko arazir aghuiba bagha bar akonge.
\ip Tesalonikan gumazamizir kaba, Krais manmaghɨn ua izamin bizim, me ti deravɨra fozir puvatɨ. Me kamaghɨn foghasa, gumazir Krais tɨghar ua izamin dughiamɨn ovengeziba, me uaghan zurara itir ikɨrmɨrir aghuim iniam, o puvatɨgham? Eghtɨ Krais dughiar manamra izam? Pol men azangsɨziba ikiarvagha kamaghɨn mɨgei, me arazir aghuibar gɨn mangɨva, Ekiam izamin dughiam bagh uari akɨr ikɨ.
\c 1
\ms1 Pol a ko ingarir darazi, me Tesalonikan itir sios gɨnɨghnɨsi
\mr (Sapta 1-3)
\p 
\v 1 Kɨ Pol, ko Sailas ko Timoti, e Tesalonikan itir sios bagha akɨnafarir kam osiri, me God Afeziam ko Ekiam Krais Iesusɨn poroghav itir gumazamiziba: Godɨn apangkuvim ko navir amɨrɨzim ia ko ikɨ.
\s1 Pol Tesalonikan itir siosɨn nɨghnɨzir gavgavim bagha bar akonge
\p 
\v 2 E zurazurara God mɨnabaghava ia bagha God ko mɨgei.
\v 3 E ian arazibagh nɨghnɨgha e fo, ia nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Godɨn itima, bizir kam ia gamima ia ingangarir aghuibagh ami. Egha ia igharazibagh ifuegha, ezɨ bizir kam ia gamima, ia pamtem ingari. Egha ia en Ekiam Krais Iesusɨn mɨzua iti, egha ia uan naviba gavgavim dagh anɨghavɨra iti. E ian arazir kaba Godɨn damazimɨn dagh nɨghnɨsi. Kamaghɨn amizɨ bizir kaba bagha e God mɨnabavɨra iti.
\p 
\v 4 En adarasi, e kamaghɨn fo, God bar moghɨra ia gifongegha, egha ua baghavɨra ia amɨsevegha gɨfa.
\v 5 Akar aghuir e inigha ia bagha izezim, an akar kɨnimɨn mɨn ia bagha izezir puvatɨ. A Godɨn Duam ko gavgavim sara ize, kamaghɨn amizɨ, ia guizbangɨra fo, akar kam a bar guizɨn akam. E ian tongɨn ikiava ian akuraghasava amizir arazim, ia uari a gɨfo.
\v 6 Egha ia Godɨn akam inizɨ, ezɨ osɨmtɨzir avɨriba ia batifi, ezɨ ia Ekiamɨn araziba ko en arazibar gɨn zuima, Godɨn Duam ian navibagh amima ia bar akonge.
\v 7 Kamaghɨn ia arazir aghuim Masedonia ko Akaian Provinsɨn itir Kraisɨn adarazi, bar men aka. Eghtɨ me ian arazimɨn ganɨva an gɨn mangam.
\v 8 Ezɨ Ekiamɨn akar ia kunizim, a dɨbɨarimɨn araremɨn mɨn bar ghu. Egha a Masedonia ko Akaiara ghuzɨ puvatɨ, ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavir Godɨn itir kamɨn eghaghanim, nguibaba bar a baraki. Kamaghɨn amizɨ, markɨ e ua me mɨkɨman kogham.
\v 9 Ezɨ dughiar e ia bagha iziba, me uari bizir otivizibar gun e geghari. Egha ia godɨn ifavariba ategha navibagh iragha guizbangɨra Godɨn gɨn zuir arazibar me geghari. A guizbangɨra ko zurara itir God.
\v 10 Ezɨ ia an Otarimɨn mɨzuai, a Godɨn Nguibam ategh uamategham. Otarir kam aremezɨma God a gamizɨ, a ua dɨkafi. A Iesus, an en akurvasi, egh dughiar Godɨn anɨngagharim izamim, an en akuragham.
\c 2
\s1 Pol Tesalonikan nguibamɨn ikiava amizir ingangarim mɨgei
\p 
\v 1 En adarasi, ia uari fo, ingangarir e ian tongɨn ikiava amizim, a pura ghuzɨ puvatɨ.
\v 2 Ia fo, e tɨghar ia bagh izamin dughiam, e Filipain nguibar ekiamɨn ikia mɨzaziba isi, ezɨ me en ziabagh asɨghasɨsi. Ezɨ dughiar e ia bagha izezim, en God en naviba gavgavim dagh anɨngizɨma, ezɨ e uan apanir avɨrir kabar atiatir puvatɨ. E tugha gavgavigha Godɨn akar aghuim ia mɨkɨri.
\v 3 Egha e ia nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Kraisɨn ikiasava, e ia mɨgɨa, egha pazav akatamɨn ia mɨkemezɨ puvatɨ, egha e nɨghnɨzir zuezir puvatɨzitam sara ia mɨgɨa ia gifarazir puvatɨ.
\v 4 Bar puvatɨ. En nɨghnɨzim a igharagha iti. God en navir averiabagh fogha gɨvagha, egha a uabɨ ifongegha akar aghuim akunamin ingangarim e ganɨngi. E gumazamiziba en ingangarim gifueghasa, e akam akurir puvatɨ. Godra en navir averiabar gari. Ezɨ e kamagh sua, a uabɨra e amir ingangarim gifongegh.
\v 5 Ia fogha gɨfa, God en garava e gɨfozɨma e kamaghɨn ia mɨgei, e akar ifavaritamɨn ia gifarazir puvatɨ, egha e ian bizibagh ifuegha egha ia apezepera mɨgeir puvatɨ.
\v 6 E, ia ko gumazamizir igharazibar damazimɨn ziam iniasa ingangarir puvatɨ.
\p 
\v 7 E guizbangɨra Kraisɨn aposelbar mɨn iti. Kamaghɨn e ti ifuegha, egha uarir akurvaghasava biziba bagha ia mɨgɨai. Egha e ingangarir ekiam ia danɨngan aghua. E bar nɨmɨra ia ko ikiava ian asughasusi. Kamaghɨra amebam uan borir aghɨriba asughasugha deragha men gari moghɨn e deravɨra ian gari.
\v 8 Ia bar guizbangɨra en namakaba, kamaghɨn amizɨma, e guizbangɨra bar ia gifonge, egha Godɨn akar aghuim ia mɨkɨmasa, egha e uaghan uan ikɨrɨmɨrim ian akurvaghasa.
\p 
\v 9 En adarasi, ia uari en ingangarir ekiar e ia ko ikia Godɨn akar aghuir kunizim gɨfo. E ghaze, e daghebar uarir akurvaghsɨ osɨmtɨzir ekiam ia danɨngan kogham. Egha e dɨmagariba ko aruebar bar puvɨra ingari.
\p 
\v 10 Ia fo, ezɨ God uaghan fo, arazir manam e ia gami, ia nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Kraisɨn itir gumazamiziba. E Godɨn damazimɨn derazir arazir aghuibagh amua, egha arazir kuratam gamizir puvatɨ.
\v 11 Ia fo, afeziam uan boribagh amir arazibar mɨrara e uaghan vaghvagha dar ia gami.
\v 12 Egha e ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavim damutɨ ia tugh gavgavighamin mɨgɨrɨgɨabagh ami. Egha ia osɨmtɨziba aterir dughiamɨn e agharim ia ganɨdi. Egha e ikɨrɨmɨrir aghuir God uabɨ ifongezimɨn gɨn mangasa ia mɨgei. God Bizibagh Ativir Dughiam oto, ezɨ a ian dia ghaze, ia dughiar kamɨn aven izɨ nan apengan ikɨva na ko pɨn ikɨ, dabirabir aghuarim nan Nguibamɨn a iniam.
\s1 Kraisɨn adarazi nɨghnɨzir gavgavim ikia, osɨmtɨziba atera tugha gavgafi
\p 
\v 13 Ia en akam baregha Godɨn akam inigha egha gumazibar akamɨn mɨn a inizir puvatɨ, ia guizbangɨra Godɨn akamra ini. Ezɨ akar kam bar pamten ia gumazamizir nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Kraisɨn itibar navir averiabar ingari. Kamaghɨn amizɨma e bizir kam bagha zurara God mɨnabi.
\v 14 En adarasi, Godɨn siosɨn Judian Provinsɨn itiba, me Krais Iesusɨn adarasi, bizir me batozibara, da uaghan ia batifi. Ian nguibamɨn gumazibara osɨmtɨzir ekiaba ia ganɨdi moghɨra, Judian itir siosba, Judaba osɨmtɨziba me garɨsi.
\v 15 Judaba, Ekiam Iesus koma Godɨn akam inigha izir gumazibav soghezɨma me ariaghɨre, egha uaghan e batosi. Egha God ifongezir arazibar aghuaghava, me gumazamiziba bar, men apanimɨn iti.
\v 16 Egha me God ua gumazamizir kaba inian me aghuagha, egha kamaghɨn e Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba akam e me mɨkɨman me aghuagha, egha en tuaviba apɨri. Kamaghɨra me zurara arazir kurabagh amima, da ghua bar ekefe, ezɨ datɨrɨghɨn Godɨn anɨngazim men izegha gɨfa.
\s1 Pol ua Tesalonikabar ganasa bar ifonge
\p 
\v 17 En adarasi, Judaba kaghɨra e arɨzima, e dughiar bar otevimɨn ia ataki, egha e ian garir puvatɨ, ezɨ en nɨghnɨziba ia ko iti. Ezɨ e ua mangɨ ian ganasa bar ifuegha egha tuaviba buriavɨra iti.
\v 18 E ia bagh izasa; kɨ Pol guizbangɨra dughiar avɨribar izasa ingari, ezɨ Satan en tuaviba apɨri.
\v 19 Eghtɨ en Ekiam Iesus uamateghamin dughiam, bizir tizim e damightɨ e an damatuzimɨn bar akuegh egh a mɨzuam ikɨ tugh gavgavigham? E bizir tizim inigh mangɨ an akagh suam e ingangarir aghuim gami? E ghaze, iarara. E ia baghavɨra bar akuegham.
\v 20 Guizbangɨra, e ia baghavɨra bar akuegham. Ezɨ iarara e gamima e bar akueghavɨra iti.
\c 3
\s1 Pol Tesalonikaba gavgavim me danɨngasa Timoti amada
\p 
\v 1 E ia bagha nɨghnɨghavɨra ikia ghua, gɨn e ghaze, e sughsughan kogham. Egha akam mɨsuegha ghaze, ga Atensɨn ikiam.
\v 2 Egha Timoti amadazɨma a ia bagha izi. Timoti a en aveghbuam. Egha a Godɨn ingangarir gumazir Kraisɨn akar aghuim akurim. Ga gavgavim ia danɨngɨva, egha ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavimɨn akurvaghasa ga anemada.
\v 3 E kamaghɨn aghua, osɨmtɨziba ko mɨzazir ia isir kaba ia damutɨ ia nɨghnɨzir avɨribar amuam. Ia uari fo, God uabɨ osɨmtɨzir kamagh gariba aterasa e amɨsefe.
\v 4 E faragha ia ko ikia egha kamagh ia mɨgɨavɨra iti, osɨmtɨzitaba e bativam. Ezɨ ia datɨrɨghɨn deragha kamaghɨn fo, dughiar kurar kam e bato.
\v 5 Bizir kam baghava, kɨ sughsughan aghuagha, egha kɨ Timoti ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavim gɨfoghasa ia bagha anemadazɨ a izi. Kɨ kamagh atiati, gumazir kuram Satan ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavibar amutɨ, da ireghtɨ, en ingangarim pura mangɨgham.
\s1 Timoti mɨgɨrɨgɨar aghuim inigha izezɨma Pol bar akonge.
\p 
\v 6 Ezɨ Timoti ia ategha egha datɨrɨghɨra iza e batogha, akar aghuim e mɨgɨa ghaze, ia nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Godɨn ikiava God ko gumazir igharazibagh ifonge. Egha a kamaghɨn mɨgɨa ghaze, ia zurara e gɨnɨghnɨgha egha ian naviba bar en dera. Egha ia en ganasava ami moghɨn e uaghan ian ganasava ami.
\v 7 Kamaghɨn amizɨma, en adarasi, dughiar e osɨmtɨziba aterima nɨghnɨzir avɨriba e bativimɨn, e kamaghɨn oraki, ia nɨghnɨzir gavgavir Godɨn itim ikiavɨra iti; ezɨ bizir kam gavgavim e ganɨngi.
\v 8 E kamaghɨn fo, ia Ekiam bagha tugha gavgavizɨma, ezɨ e kagh uaghan, en dabirabim datɨrɨghɨn bar dera.
\v 9 E ia gɨnɨghnɨgha egha e uan Godɨn damazimɨn guizbangɨra bar akonge. Kamaghɨn amizɨ, e ia bagha God bar mɨnabavɨra iti.
\v 10 Egha dɨmagariba ko aruebar, God ko pamtem mɨgɨavɨra ikia ghaze, God en amamangatɨghtɨ e uari izɨ ian ganam. Eghtɨ ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavim oteveghtɨ, e ua ian akurvaghɨva ian nɨghnɨzir gavgavim damutɨma, a gavgavigham.
\s1 Pol God ko mɨgei
\p 
\v 11 E kamagh sua, en God en Afeziam uabɨ ko Iesus en Ekiam, e bagh tuavim azeneghtɨ e ia bagh izam.
\v 12 E kamagh sua, Ekiam ia damightɨ arazir igharazir darazigh ifongezim bar moghɨra ia gizɨfagh egh fasfagham. E bar ia gifongezɨ moghɨra, ia vaghvagh Godɨn gumazamiziba ko gumazamizir igharaziba bar me gifongegh.
\v 13 Eghtɨ God gavgavim ia danɨngtɨ, gumazamizir en Ekiam Iesusɨn damazimɨn zueziba bar, a ko uamateghtɨ, en God en Afeziam ian gantɨma ia an damazimɨn zuegh arazir kuraba puvatɨgham.
\c 4
\ms1 Tesalonikabar arazir aghuiba men ikɨrɨmɨrimɨn aven otogh egh gavgafigh
\mr (Sapta 4-5)
\s1 E gumazamiziba uari bakɨa uari ko akuir arazim damuam kogham
\p 
\v 1 Kamaghɨn, en adarazi, e God ifongezir araziba bar ian akagha ghaze, arazir kaba ia dar amu. Arazir kaba, ia datɨrɨghɨn guizbangɨra dagh ami. E datɨrɨghɨn Ekiam Iesusɨn ziamɨn gavgavimɨn ia gakaghora ghaze, ia arazir kabar amu mamaghɨra ikɨ.
\v 2 E Ekiam Iesusɨn ziamɨn ian sure gamizir akaba, ia dagh fo.
\p 
\v 3 God kamaghɨn ifonge, ia bar uari isɨva a danigh egh an damazimɨn zuegh. Egh gumazamiziba tintinibar uari isava akuir arazim gitagham.
\v 4 Egh ia vaghvagh uan amuibar ikɨva deravɨra men gan. Egh Godɨn damazimɨn zuezir araziba ko a ifongezir arazibar amu.\f + \ft (4:4) Marazi ghaze, vezɨn kam kamaghɨn ghu: “Ia uan ifongiaba ko nɨghnɨzir kurar ian navir averiabar aven itiba, ia deraghvɨra da bagh uarir gan. Egh Godɨn damazimɨn zuezir araziba ko a ifongezir arazibar amu.”\f*
\v 5 Ia uan mɨkarzimɨn ifongiabara, dar gɨn mangan markɨ, mati God gɨfozir puvatɨzir gumaziba amir araziba.
\v 6 Kamaghɨn ia uan aveghbuaba osɨmtɨziba me darɨgh egh me gifar arazir kurabar men amuibar amuan markɨ. E fomɨra akar gavgavim ia mɨgɨa ghaze, gumazir arazir kurar kabanagh gamiba, God gɨn ivezir kuram me danɨngam.
\v 7 E fo, God arazir mɨzɨrɨziba bagha en diazir pu. Bar puvatɨ. A en diagha ghaze, ia nan gumazamizibara, kamaghɨn ia arazir zuezibara damu.
\v 8 Kamaghɨn amizɨ, nɨ tina akar kaba akɨrim dagh asara, nɨ akɨrim gumazim gasarazir puvatɨ, nɨ God akɨrim a gasara, Godɨn kamra uan Duam ia ganɨngi.
\s1 E arazir aghuibar amutɨ da gavgavika
\p 
\v 9 Kɨ Kraisɨn adarasi uarigh ifongezir arazimɨn kɨ ia bagh osiran kogham. Kɨ fo, God uabɨ ia uarigh ifueghamin arazim bagha ian sure gami.
\v 10 Ezɨ ia Provins Masedonian itir Kraisɨn adarasi uarigh ifongezir arazibar bar me gami. En adarasi, e ia arazir kam damu mangɨ mamaghɨra ikiasa e ian azangsɨsi.
\p 
\v 11-12 Kɨ kamagh sua, ia bizitamɨn oteveghan kogham, eghtɨ gumazir Kraisɨn azenan itiba ian ganɨva egh kamaghɨn mɨkɨm suam, Kraisɨn adarasi arazir aghuibagh ami. Bizir kam bagh ia uan dabirabir amɨrizim damutɨ a deraghsɨ, puvɨra uari bagh ingar. Egh uan agharibar uari ingar egh ia uari uarir akurvagham, kamaghɨra e fomɨra ia mɨkemes.
\s1 Ekiam uamategh izɨva e akuvagham
\p 
\v 13 En adarasi, e kamagh sua, ia bar deravɨra Kraisɨn gumazamizir ovengeziba bativamin bizim gɨfogh. Ia gumazir igharazir nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Godɨn itir puvatɨzibar mɨn pamten osemegh ikian markɨ. Me ua dɨkavamin dughiam mɨzuair puvatɨ.
\v 14 E kamaghɨn nɨghnɨzir gavgavim iti. Iesus aremegha ua dɨkafi. Kamaghɨn amizɨ, en nɨghnɨzir gavgavim kamaghɨn, God gumazir nɨghnɨzir gavgavim an ikiava ovengezibar amightɨ, me ua dɨkavigh egh Iesus ko ua izam.
\p 
\v 15 Ekiamɨn akam e kamaghɨn ia mɨkeme, Ekiam uamateghtɨma e gumazamizir angamra itiba, gumazir ariaghrezibar faragh mangan kogham. Puvatɨ.
\v 16 Ekiam pamtem mɨkɨmtɨ, an enselɨn faragha zuimɨn tiarim mɨkɨmtɨ, eghtɨ Godɨn sɨgham sara arangam. Eghtɨ Ekiamra uan nguibam ategh izɨghɨrɨtɨma gumazamizir Iesusɨn poroghav ikiava ariaghreziba faragh ua dɨkavigham.
\v 17 Dughiar kamɨn gɨn e gumazamizir angamra ikiavɨra itiba, e gumazamizir kaba ko ghuariabar tongɨn mavanangam, egh e bar Ekiam overiamɨn a bativam. Kamaghɨn e bar Ekiam ko zurazurara ikiam.
\v 18 Egh ia akar kam Godɨn gumazamizir igharazibav kɨm, egh gavgavim uari danɨng.
\c 5
\s1 E Ekiam izamin dughiam bagh uari akɨr ikiam
\p 
\v 1 En adarasi, e bizir otivamin dughiatam dɨborogh ia bagh an osirighan kogham.
\v 2 Ia uari fogha gɨfa, Ekiam Izamin Dughiam okɨmakɨar gumazim dɨmangan izi moghɨn zuamɨrama otogham. A izamin dughiam, ia a gɨfoghan kogham.
\v 3 Gumazamiziba kamaghɨn mɨkɨmam, “Datɨrɨghɨn dughiar amɨrizim e batozɨ, e deravɨra iti.” Eghtɨ bizir me gasɨghasɨghamim bar zuamɨra me batogham, mati mɨzazir amizir naviba adaiba borim batasa isir mɨzaziba. Men tav osɨmtɨzir kam gitagh arɨ mangan kogham.
\p 
\v 4 Kamaghɨn amizɨ en adarasi, ia mɨtatemɨn itir puvatɨ, egh ia, dughiar kam okɨmakɨar gumazimɨn mɨn izɨtɨ, ia an ganigh dɨgavir kuram damuan kogham.
\v 5 Ia fo, ia bar aruem ko angazangarimɨn gumazamiziba. E dɨmagarim ko mɨtatemɨn adarasi puvatɨ.
\v 6 Kamaghɨn amizɨ, e gumazir igharazibar mɨn daku ikian kogham. En damaziba kuighreghtɨma e deraghvɨra nɨghnɨgham.
\v 7 E fo, gumazir akuiba me dɨmagaribar akui. Ezɨ gumazir dɨpar kuraba apa onganiziba, dɨmagaribar da api.
\v 8 Ezɨ e aruemɨn adarazi, kamaghɨn e deraghvɨra nɨghnɨgham. E nɨghnɨzir gavgavim Godɨn itir arazim ko igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim nigham. Egh bizir kamning inighɨva mɨdorozir korotiamɨn mɨn uan evariba ikeghtɨ da e apazagham. Egh Godɨn mɨzuam ikɨ an akurvazir arazim inigh, e mɨdorozir dapanir asuamɨn mɨn anerughtɨ an e apazagham.
\v 9 God, uan anɨngagharimɨn aven mangasa e amɨsevezir puvatɨ. A en Ekiam Krais Iesusɨn ingangarimɨn en akurvaghasa e amɨsefe.
\v 10 Iesus en akurvaghasava e bagha areme. Kamaghɨn amizɨ, e ovenge, o e angamra iti, e a ko angamra ikiam.
\v 11 Kamaghɨn amizɨ, ia uari vaghvagh akar aghuibar uariv kɨm egh gavgavim uari danɨng, mati ia datɨrɨghɨn ami moghɨn.
\s1 God uan adarazir akuraghtɨ me arazir aghuibar amuam
\p 
\v 12 En adarasi, e kamaghɨn ian azangsɨsi, ia gumazir ian akurvagha ia ko ingaribar apengan ikɨ. Ekiam ian gumazir dapanibar ikiasa me amɨsefe, eghtɨ me ian araziba akɨramin mɨgɨrɨgɨabar amuam.
\v 13 Ia men ingangarir me amir kam gɨnɨghnɨgh, egh naviba bar men deraghɨva me gifongeghɨva egh men apengan ikɨ. Egh ia bar uari inigh navir amɨrɨzimɨn ikɨ.
\p 
\v 14 En adarasi, e kamaghɨn ian azangsɨghasa, ia gumazamizir amɨrɨzibar araziba akɨriva, egh gumazamizir atiatiabar naviba gavgavim me danɨngɨva, egh gumazamizir gavgaviba puvatɨziba akurvagh, egh ia gumazamiziba bar dughorir amɨrizim men ikɨ.
\p 
\v 15 Ia deravɨra gan, gumazitam arazir kurabar ia damutɨma, ia an arazir kuraba ikaravaghan markɨ. Ia zurara arazir aghuibar Godɨn gumazamizibar amusɨ gavgavigh, egh uaghan gumazamizir igharaziba sara.
\p 
\v 16 Egh ia zurara bar akongegh,
\v 17 egh ia God ko zurara mɨkɨmvɨra ikɨ.
\v 18 Bizir tizim ia bato, God mɨnabɨvɨra ikɨ. God kamagh sua, ia gumazamizir Krais Iesusɨn poroghav itiba ia arazir kaba bar, dar amu.
\p 
\v 19 Eghtɨ Godɨn Duam bizitam damusɨ ia mɨkɨmtɨma, ia an anogoroghan markɨ.
\v 20 Eghtɨ ia Godɨn akam inigha izir gumazibar akam me ia mɨkɨmtɨma ia navir kuram men ikian markɨ.
\v 21 Egh ia bar deravɨra araziba ko akaba bar, da tuisɨgh. Egh arazir aghuibara, ia dar suigh.
\v 22 Egh arazir kuraba ia bar da atakigh.
\p 
\v 23 God uabɨ navir amɨrɨzimɨn mɨngarim, a ia damightɨma ia uari isɨ bar a danɨng, egh an damazimɨn bar zuegham. Eghtɨ a ian duaba ko, mɨkarziba ko, ikɨrɨmɨriba bar moghɨra deraghvɨra dar gantɨ, da deraghvɨra ikɨva en Ekiam Krais Iesus izamin dughiamɨn ia arazir kuratam Godɨn damazimɨn bar puvatɨgham.
\v 24 Godɨn ian diazim, a uan akabar gɨn ghua bizibagh amima da guizɨn otifi. Kamaghɨn e fo, a guizbangɨra bizir kabar amuam.
\b
\p 
\v 25 En adarasi, ia e bagh God ko mɨkɨmtɨ, a en akuraka.
\p 
\v 26 Ia Kraisɨn gumazamiziba, vaghvagh uan dafaribar suigh.
\p 
\v 27 Kɨ Ekiamɨn ziamɨn akɨnafarir kam Kraisɨn gumazamiziba bar me bagh a dɨpon me mɨkɨmasa ia gakaghori.
\p 
\v 28 En Ekiam Krais Iesusɨn apangkuvim bar moghɨra ia ko ikɨ.
